The '''''Vagabond Trader''''' was an [[SX troop transport]] stolen from [[Dellalt/Legends|Dellalt]] by a group of fugitive [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] and subsequently docked in the [[Hangar/Legends|hangar]] bay of the ''[[Drunk Dancer]]''. It was later disguised as a civilian [[Starship/Legends|ship]] and christened the ''Vagabond Trader'' in an attempt to fool [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] Commerce Control and ferry [[Olee Starstone]] and her fellow Jedi to Kashyyyk. Upon arrival on the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] planet, [[Cudgel (Human)|Cudgel]] identified the ''Trader'' as an L-200.

